  "text": "In order to evaluate our hypothesis that a consistent gallery between training and testing gives machine learning based [CITATION_1] versus machine learning-based meta-recognition accuracy for a controlled synthetic data set reflecting the portfolio model. Machine learning-based algorithm shows a clear advantage over the pure statistical algorithm when a consistent gallery is considered for training and testing. When the machine learning classifier is trained and tested using different galleries, performance is approximate to that of the statistical algorithm.",
